DataList.LocalizeJP: はぁ……ブルーアーカイブ……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Ha~ Blue Archive...

DataList.LocalizeKR:
하아, 어쩌다 이렇게 되어버린 걸까요.
뭐, 이렇게 된 이상, 해야 할 일은 하겠지만요.
DataList.LocalizeJP:
はあ、どうしてこんなことに……。
まあこうなった以上、やることはやりますよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN:
Ha~ Why did this happen?
Hm~ Now that it's like this, I'll do what I have to do.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
静かに本を
読めるところは……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Where I can quietly read a book...

DataList.LocalizeJP:
あぁ、
めんどくさい……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Aa... It's troublesome...

DataList.LocalizeJP:
あんまり
騒がしいのは
ちょっと……
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's a little noisy...

DataList.LocalizeJP:
どこか、
バレなさそうな
ところは……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Do you know anywhere I can hide?

DataList.LocalizeKR:
과연, 여기라면
들키지 않을 것 같네요.
DataList.LocalizeJP:
なるほど、ここなら
見つからないかも
しれませんね
DataList.LocalizeEN: Oh I see, I can't be seen here.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
はぁ、
何ですか当番制って……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Ha~ What is this duty system?

DataList.LocalizeJP:
はいはい、
頼まれたからには頑張りますよ
DataList.LocalizeEN: Fine, I'll do my best since you asked.

DataList.LocalizeKR:
아아… 어서 오세요. 선생님.
자, 귀찮은 일이
잔뜩 기다리고 있다구요.
DataList.LocalizeJP:
ああ……おかえりなさい、先生
ほら、めんどうな仕事が
山積みですよ
DataList.LocalizeEN: Welcome back, Sensei. Look, there's a lot of troublesome work.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ふぅ……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Hm...

DataList.LocalizeKR:
살짝 딴 데서
농땡이 부리지 않을래요?
DataList.LocalizeJP:
ちょっとどこかで
サボりません？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Would you like to skip somewhere for a moment?

DataList.LocalizeJP: ……ちゃんとやってますよ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: ...I have to do it properly?

DataList.LocalizeJP:
めんどくさいですが……
はぁ、仕方ありませんね
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's troublesome... Ha, but it needs to be done.

DataList.LocalizeKR:
뭔가요.
해야 할 일은
다 끝내뒀는데요.
DataList.LocalizeJP:
何ですか。
やるべきことは、
ちゃんと終わらせましたが
DataList.LocalizeEN: What is it? I finished what I had to do.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
どうしました、
何か頼み事でも？
DataList.LocalizeEN: What's wrong? Do you need something?

DataList.LocalizeKR:
그런 표정 안 지으셔도,
오늘이 선생님의 생일이라는
건 알고 있어요.
DataList.LocalizeJP:
そんな顔しなくても、
今日が先生の誕生日って
ことくらい知ってます
DataList.LocalizeEN: You don't need to make that face, I know that today is Sensei's birthday.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
……仕方ありませんね、
祝ってあげますよ
DataList.LocalizeEN: It can't be helped.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
お誕生日
おめでとうございます、先生
DataList.LocalizeEN: I wish you a happy birthday, Sensei.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
……はい？私の誕生日……
どこでそれを……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Yes? My birthday?

DataList.LocalizeJP:
いえ、
別に嫌というわけでは……
DataList.LocalizeEN: No, it's not that I don't like it...

DataList.LocalizeKR:
잠깐 떨어져 주세요.
지금은 다가오지
말아주세요….
DataList.LocalizeJP:
ちょっとあっち行ってて
ください、今は近寄ら
ないでもらえると
DataList.LocalizeEN: Please go away for a moment, and if you could stay away from me.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
あけまして
おめでとうございます
DataList.LocalizeEN: Happy New Year.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
そうですね、
願うことがあるとすれば……
DataList.LocalizeEN: A wish for new year?

DataList.LocalizeKR:
올해는 귀찮은 일이,
가능한 한 적었으면
좋겠네요.
DataList.LocalizeJP:
今年は面倒ごとが、
できるだけ少ないと
良いですね
DataList.LocalizeEN: Let me see, it would be nice to have as little trouble as possible this year.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 誰も彼も浮かれてますね……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Everyone seems happy...

DataList.LocalizeJP: いえ、別に嫌というわけでは
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's not like I hate it, but I don't like going outside either.

DataList.LocalizeKR:
밖에 나가는 것도 좀 그렇고,
어쩔 수 없죠. 선생님이랑
같이 있어 드릴까요.
DataList.LocalizeJP:
外に出るのもアレですし、
仕方ないので先生と
一緒にいてあげますか……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Looks like I have no choice, I will come with you, Sensei...

DataList.LocalizeJP: はい、とっとと飴ください。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Yes, just give me candy.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ……え？ちゃんと言ってほしい？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Eh? You want me to say it properly?

DataList.LocalizeJP:
はいはい、
トリックオアトリートー
DataList.LocalizeEN: Alright, trick or treat~

DataList.LocalizeKR:
하아, 정말…. 이렇게까지 해주신다면,
저도 진심으로 할 수밖에 없잖아요.
DataList.LocalizeJP:
はぁ、全く……ここまでしてもらって、
本気を出さないわけには
いかないじゃないですか
DataList.LocalizeEN: Ha... Why did you have to go this far for me... Now I can't help but get serious.
